b_The American DJ F-Timer-Dyno II is an optional timer remote for Dyno-Fog II fog machine. It controls the fog output at designated time intervals. Three LED lights indicate different functions: Yellow - timer is turned on and is activated Red - power is on Green - Fog Output is available The remote features dual rotary knobs that turns the timer on and off and setting the length of fog output.
